Took me about an hour and a half  to complete. I would appreciate if you did not steal it, but what could I do about it? Please rate and critique my creation and I'll be open to your responses. Don't be afraid to criticize, but please refrain from profanity. Thank you -Synchrome

Post Scriptum - This is my first skin that I made in this mold and comment if I should make more.
